In a bowl, mix mayonnaise, green chile peppers, black olives, and green onion. Heat the olive oil in a skillet over medium heat. Place shrimp in skillet and cook 2 to 5 minutes, until opaque. Stir in the mayonnaise mixture and continue cooking 2 to 5 minutes, until mixture has heated through. Remove skillet from heat. Gently fold in blue cheese. Transfer dip to a serving bowl.